OL,3,CShoplifting crackdown: Third of
OL,4,Coffences result in arrest, charge or
OL,5,Cconviction
OL,7,FNew figures show nearly a third 31% of
OL,8,Fthe 1,400 shoplifting offences
OL,9,Frecorded in the City of London
OL,10,Fresulted in an arrest, charge or
OL,11,Fconviction.
OL,13,FThe figure is above national figure of
OL,14,F18.5% for England and Wales and was
OL,15,Fthe result of officers building
OL,16,F'strong relationships with retailers
OL,17,Fand businesses across the City, police
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
