FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779199898
OL,3,CShoplifting crackdown: Third of
OL,4,Coffences result in arrest, charge or
OL,5,Cconviction
OL,7,F"When they have confidence their
OL,8,Freports will be acted on, offenders
OL,9,Fpursued and outcomes achieved, they
OL,10,Fare far more likely to come forward
OL,11,Fand work with us," City of London
OL,12,FPolice Commissioner Pete O'Doherty
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779199898
OL,3,CShoplifting crackdown: Third of
OL,4,Coffences result in arrest, charge or
OL,5,Cconviction
OL,7,F"Tackling shoplifting and other
OL,8,Facquisitive crime is a priority for
OL,9,Fthe City of London Police and these
OL,10,Ffigures demonstrate that our officers,
OL,11,Fsupported by advanced CCTV and
OL,12,Fintelligence-led policing, are
OL,13,Fidentifying offenders, making arrests
OL,14,Fand protecting the businesses and
OL,15,Fvictims."
OL,17,FAs part of their Safer City Streets
OL,18,Flaunch, the City of London Police are
OL,19,Fintroducing newly branded police boxes
OL,20,Facross the Square Mile, modernising
OL,21,Fthe former "ring of steel" for 2026.
OL,26,@}D@LOU}D@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779199898
OL,3,CShoplifting crackdown: Third of
OL,4,Coffences result in arrest, charge or
OL,5,Cconviction
OL,7,FTo boost police visibility, each box
OL,8,Fwill feature officers who patrol the
OL,9,Fsquare mile on foot and bike.
OL,11,FTijs Broeke, City of London Police
OL,12,FAuthority Board Chair, said: "Retail
OL,13,Fcrime, including shoplifting, is a
OL,14,Fblight on businesses across the Square
OL,15,FMile, undermining confidence and
OL,16,Faffecting staff every day.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779199898
OL,3,CShoplifting crackdown: Third of
OL,4,Coffences result in arrest, charge or
OL,5,Cconviction
OL,7,F"Tackling it must be a priority. Safer
OL,8,FCity Streets shows what can be
OL,9,Fachieved through visible policing,
OL,10,Ftargeted action, smart use of
OL,11,Ftechnology and a pro-active approach
OL,12,Fto protecting businesses and
OL,13,Fidentifying offenders."
OL,15,FPaul Michael Whitehead, 46, of no
OL,16,Ffixed abode, pleaded guilty to three
OL,17,Fcounts of theft after stealing over
OL,18,F#1,000 worth of perfume.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779199898
OL,3,CShoplifting crackdown: Third of
OL,4,Coffences result in arrest, charge or
OL,5,Cconviction
OL,7,FOn 17th April 2026, City of London
OL,8,FPolice control room officers were
OL,9,Falerted after store staff recognised
OL,10,FWhitehead, who had stolen from the
OL,11,Fshop days earlier.
OL,13,FThe City of London Police are one of
OL,14,Fthe only forces in the country who can
OL,15,Fcontrol and operate the CCTV cameras.
OL,17,FControl room officers tracked
OL,18,FWhitehead's movements, where he
OL,19,Fentered a supermarket and stole two
OL,20,Fbottles of wine, while directing
OL,21,Fresponse officers to his location.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779199898
OL,3,CShoplifting crackdown: Third of
OL,4,Coffences result in arrest, charge or
OL,5,Cconviction
OL,7,FWhitehead was arrested and later
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty to theft offences
OL,9,Fcommitted on 14 and 15th April, where
OL,10,Fhe forced open perfume cabinets and
OL,11,Fstole products worth more than #1,200
OL,12,Fin total.
OL,14,FHe has been remanded in custody and
OL,15,Fwill be sentenced in June.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779199898
OL,3,CShoplifting crackdown: Third of
OL,4,Coffences result in arrest, charge or
OL,5,Cconviction
OL,7,FThe City's CCTV network remains one of
OL,8,Fthe most advanced policing assets in
OL,9,Fthe country, allowing officers and
OL,10,Fcontrol room staff to track suspects
OL,11,Fin real time, direct resources
OL,12,Fimmediately and protect businesses,
OL,13,Fworkers and the public.
OL,15,FThe force has invested Home Office
OL,16,Ffunding to analyse crime data and
OL,17,Fembed hotspot policing as a permanent
OL,18,Fstrategy, providing officers with data-
OL,19,Fled briefings on precisely when and
OL,20,Fwhere to carry out highly visible
OL,21,Fpatrols to maximise crime reduction.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779199898
OL,3,CShoplifting crackdown: Third of
OL,4,Coffences result in arrest, charge or
OL,5,Cconviction
OL,7,FAdding to its CCTV network, the force
OL,8,Fis adding new cameras in hotspot areas
OL,9,Fto better detect criminals.
OL,11,FHot spot policing has already shown
OL,12,Fresults between February 2025 and
OL,13,FFebruary 2026:
OL,15,FThe force also continues to invest in
OL,16,Ftechnology including the Image
OL,17,FRecognition and Identification System,
OL,18,Fwhich allows officers to identify
OL,19,Fsuspects using searchable tagged
OL,20,Fimages, helping secure faster arrests
OL,21,Fand prosecutions.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
